These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, corn, lime, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, magic-tricks, puzzles, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, spy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, soul, ambient, indie
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, goldfish, goat
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the fan of jazz is the person eating onion##1
 6. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is the person eating onion##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching fantasy movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | corn    | lime      | onion  | pomegranate     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking    | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy       | martial-arts | spy     | mystery    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | soul         | jazz  | ambient    |
| Pet           | goldfish      | goat       | cat | fish |

