.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, sprite, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel, action, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, jazz, techno
4 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, cat, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, rowing, rugby
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 2. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the fan of techno##1
 9. the person watching action movies is the fan of jazz##1
10. the fan of country is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | lemonade     | sprite    | juice |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel   | action   | crime           |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | techno     | jazz    | country         |
| Pet           | goldfish         | rabbit | cat     | dog        |
| Sport         | lacrosse     | rugby  | cycling | rowing       |

