.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, strawberry, corn, banana
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, german, thai
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, climbing, volleyball, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, jet-ski, airplane
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person eating corn is the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person eating corn##1
 7. the german is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the thai is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the colombian is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
12. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | artichoke    | banana      | corn  | strawberry   |
| Nationality   | thai     | german      | colombian | brazilian      |
| Pet           | chinchilla       | hedgehog         | turtle  | hamster         |
| Sport         | cycling | climbing | volleyball  | parkour |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | skateboard         | airplane   | quad-bike        |

