.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, 7up, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, peach, lime, tomato
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, french, indian, british
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, fish, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, helicopter, scooter
 1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the british is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the right of the indian##1
 9. the french is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | 7up   | iced-tea   | tea      | hot-chocolate     |
| Food          | lime     | lettuce   | tomato | peach |
| Nationality   | french | indian | malaysian   | british       |
| Pet           | bird       | hamster      | hedgehog     | fish |
| Transport     | tram    | helicopter     | scooter     | motorbike     |

