 1. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the designer is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person drinking water is the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the car##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is the lawyer##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the car##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the engineer is on the left of the lawyer##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
