 8. the person driving the ship is on the right of the freelancer##1
 9. the person drinking juice is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person drinking tea is the owner of the horse##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | juice     | iced-tea  | tea       | 7up      |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks    | dancing        | gardening  | fishing      |
| Job         | freelancer  | mechanic | coach | writer |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | rabbit          | horse         | fish      |
| Transport   | bike     | ship     | roller       | airplane          |

