.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, sudoku, skydiving, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, romance, spy, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, argentine, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, turtle, frog
 1. the argentine is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the nigerian is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
