.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, carrot, spinach, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, woodworking, skydiving, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, adventure, animation, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, swimming, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, train, quad-bike, van
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating spinach##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person eating onion##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
