.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, apple, garlic, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, hiking, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, coach, dressmaker, chef
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, dog, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, van, airplane, taxi
 1. the chef is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 3. the chef is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the librarian##1
 5. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the coach##1
 8. the librarian is the person driving the helicopter##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person eating spinach is the owner of the hamster##1
11. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | apple    | spinach        | lettuce        | garlic      |
| Hobby       | hiking       | woodworking       | gardening      | magic-tricks |
| Job         | coach | chef | dressmaker | librarian      |
| Pet         | hedgehog          | hamster         | chinchilla           | dog    |
| Transport   | airplane         | van       | taxi     | helicopter   |

 